00:42:23,980 --> 00:42:26,280
辛苦啦
investigating the possibility that your father

628
00:42:26,300 --> 00:42:29,600
辛苦啦
may have been involved in other, more serious crimes.

629
00:42:29,620 --> 00:42:31,880
辛苦啦
We're going to make a public appeal for information.

630
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:35,040
辛苦啦
I don't like people referring to him as my father.

631
00:42:36,940 --> 00:42:38,420
辛苦啦
OK, I'm sorry.

632
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:40,780
辛苦啦
What would you prefer?

633
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:42,100
辛苦啦
His name.

634
00:42:44,180 --> 00:42:45,620
辛苦啦
What other crimes?

635
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:48,460
辛苦啦
Four murders.

636
00:42:48,500 --> 00:42:50,820
辛苦啦
Scoveston Park and Coastal Path.

637
00:42:54,020 --> 00:42:57,410
辛苦啦
I'm not getting dragged back into all that shit again.

638
00:42:57,740 --> 00:43:00,010
辛苦啦
I told Huntsman everything I know.

639
00:43:03,340 --> 00:43:04,800
辛苦啦
He's got his father's eyes.

640
00:43:04,820 --> 00:43:06,200
辛苦啦
Yeah, I clocked that.

641
00:43:06,220 --> 00:43:08,520
辛苦啦
Why do you think he only changed his first name?

642
00:43:08,540 --> 00:43:10,720
辛苦啦
If you wanna lie low, you change your surname.

643
00:43:10,740 --> 00:43:12,720
辛苦啦
Maybe it wasn't about lying low.

644
00:43:12,740 --> 00:43:16,710
辛苦啦
He changed his name in 1998, the same year Cooper was put away.

645
00:43:16,740 --> 00:43:18,680
辛苦啦
Maybe it was about starting again.

646
00:43:18,700 --> 00:43:20,460
辛苦啦
A new name, a new life.

647
00:43:20,500 --> 00:43:22,840
辛苦啦
Doesn't look like that's working out too well for him.

648
00:43:22,860 --> 00:43:26,060
辛苦啦
- The poor guy's a wreck. - And then we come along.

649
00:44:07,140 --> 00:44:09,020
辛苦啦
- Are you OK? - Yeah.

650
00:44:11,980 --> 00:44:14,780
辛苦啦
It's just you and me having a conversation.

651
00:44:15,940 --> 00:44:17,100
辛苦啦
Yeah.

652
00:44:18,100 --> 00:44:21,110
辛苦啦
In front of a few hundred thousand people, live.

653
00:44:25,820 --> 00:44:28,100
辛苦啦
You know, in my first year at uni,

654
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:31,040
辛苦啦
me and some of my mates went camping near here.

655
00:44:31,060 --> 00:44:34,070
辛苦啦
It was July 1989. It was just after the murders.

656
00:44:35,620 --> 00:44:38,180
辛苦啦
We saw all the police activity.

657
00:44:38,220 --> 00:44:39,740
辛苦啦
The wanted posters.

658
00:44:40,940 --> 00:44:42,060
辛苦啦
It was scary.

659
00:44:43,900 --> 00:44:45,500
辛苦啦
Fascinating as well.

660
00:44:47,060 --> 00:44:50,200
辛苦啦
It's what made me want to become a crime reporter.

661
00:44:52,540 --> 00:44:53,820
辛苦啦
Good to go?

662
00:44:54,940 --> 00:44:56,620
辛苦啦
- Let's do it. - Yeah.

663
00:45:16,980 --> 00:45:18,920
辛苦啦
Good evening. We are live in Pembrokeshire,

664
00:45:18,940 --> 00:45:21,120
辛苦啦
where there have been dramatic developments

665
00:45:21,140 --> 00:45:23,560
辛苦啦
in two of Wales's most baffling crimes -

666
00:45:23,580 --> 00:45:26,040
辛苦啦
the murders of Richard and Helen Thomas,

667
00:45:26,060 --> 00:45:27,720
辛苦啦
and Peter and Gwenda Dixon.

668
00:45:27,740 --> 00:45:29,540
辛苦啦
And now, decades on,

669
00:45:29,580 --> 00:45:32,240
辛苦啦
these two double murders are being reinvestigated.

670
00:45:32,260 --> 00:45:34,280
辛苦啦
Detective Superintendent Steve Wilkins

671
00:45:34,300 --> 00:45:37,580
辛苦啦
is the man leading this reinvestigation.

672
00:45:37,620 --> 00:45:40,760
辛苦啦
Developments in DNA analysis have revolutionised cold case reviews.

673
00:45:40,780 --> 00:45:43,200
辛苦啦
As a team, we have brought these processes to bear

674
00:45:43,220 --> 00:45:44,680
辛苦啦
on these two investigations

675
00:45:44,700 --> 00:45:47,340
辛苦啦
and they have had a significant impact.

676
00:45:47,380 --> 00:45:50,720
辛苦啦
We believe that somebody watching this programme tonight

677
00:45:50,740 --> 00:45:53,360
辛苦啦
may know who is responsible for these terrible crimes.

678
00:45:53,380 --> 00:45:54,760
辛苦啦
And I'm appealing to them,

679
00:45:54,780 --> 00:45:56,960
辛苦啦
for the sake of the victims and their families,

680
00:45:56,980 --> 00:45:58,520
辛苦啦
to please come forward.

681
00:45:58,540 --> 00:46:00,720
辛苦啦
And do you think it's the same local man

682
00:46:00,740 --> 00:46:02,440
辛苦啦
responsible for all four murders?

683
00:46:02,460 --> 00:46:04,080
辛苦啦
I do believe that, Jonathan.

684
00:46:04,100 --> 00:46:06,920
辛苦啦
Thanks to the advances in DNA forensic science,

685
00:46:06,940 --> 00:46:08,480
辛苦啦
we are now in a much stronger position

686
00:46:08,500 --> 00:46:10,630
辛苦啦
to catch the person responsible.


